OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers clearing Kent, then sunny
OL,7,Fspells for many this evening. A dry
OL,8,Fnight follows with clear spells, but
OL,9,Fshowers into western parts by dawn.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FMostly cloudy with heavy
OL,12,Fshowers and sunny intervals early
OL,13,FTuesday, with a risk of hail and
OL,14,Fthunder. Sunny spells as showers ease
OL,15,Flater. Feeling cool for the time of
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
